<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBg9_00120" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBg9_00120_F001">
<paragraph>
<sentence>冴子は取り上げるとファインダーを覗い<sampling type="start" />た。</sentence>
<sentence>小さな画面で覗く世界は、一層、幻想的だった。</sentence>
<sentence>靄が厚い雲の<ruby rubyText="じゅう">絨</ruby><ruby rubyText="たん">毯</ruby>のように感じられる。</sentence>
<sentence>簡単に飛び乗れそうな気がした。</sentence>
<sentence>それができたら、どんなに楽だろう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子は階段側の手摺りに立つと、津田の姿を求めた。</sentence>
<sentence>津田は狭い坂道を登って行く。</sentence>
<sentence>気配を感じたのか、津田がこちらを向いた。</sentence>
<sentence>ビデオに気づいておどけた。</sentence>
<sentence>ズームにすると津田の顔がはっきりとした。</sentence>
<sentence>笑顔が<ruby rubyText="こお">凍</ruby>っている。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　〈さようなら…〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　不意にその言葉が浮かんで、冴子自身がうろたえた。</sentence>
<sentence>どうしてそんな不吉なことを思ったのだろうか。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　〈…！〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　角度を変えて五大堂の手摺り越しに撮影していたら、その画面に洋介が現われた。</sentence>
<sentence>夢の中とおなじに、小さな体の洋介が手摺りの上で<ruby rubyText="あぐら">胡座</ruby>をかいていた。</sentence>
<sentence>冴子の鼓動が早まった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「これも夢？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子は思わず口にした。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「どうかな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">冴子の好きなように考えろ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　洋介はニヤニヤとタバコをふかした。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「だって…おかしいわ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子はビデオを回し続けた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「どうする？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">　頑張って見るか」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「辛いのは、おまえよりも良平だぜ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どっちの場合？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「どっちでもさ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">だろ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どっちでも？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「たぶんな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">オレにはそんな気がする」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そういうことなの…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子はファインダーから目を離した。</sentence>
<sentence>洋介は哀しそうな顔をして手摺りの上を歩いた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「オレの時は<ruby rubyText="ばあ">祖母</ruby>さんが来た」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「今でも元気？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「だよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">こっちも案外居心地がいい」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「怖いわ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　それに洋介は素直に頷いた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「けど…そんなでもない」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「一緒に連れて行ってくれるの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「当たり前のことを聞くな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「良平さんはどうなるのかなぁ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あいつも来るよ…そのうちに」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おまえたちはそういう仲なんだ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">どこまで行っても赤い糸が切れやしない」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子は嬉しさに泣いた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「またおなじところで暮らすのさ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ホントに…ホントにそうなの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おまえ…兄貴の言葉を信用しないのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「だって…これ、夢でしょ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　洋介はアハハと笑った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「違うの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「答えようがないよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">こっちにだって」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「信じるわ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「雲に乗ればいい。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">それだけだ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　洋介はひょいと雲に乗った。</sentence>
<sentence>手招きをする。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「待って…良平さんに言いたいことが」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子はビデオを自分の顔に向けた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<blockEnd />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「もう充分だろ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　洋介は冴子を<ruby rubyText="せ">急</ruby>かせた。</sentence>
<sentence>ビデオに向かって良平への別れを言った冴子の顔は、すっかり落ち着いていた。</sentence>
<sentence>一筋の涙が頰を伝う。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「これでいいのよね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　涙を<ruby rubyText="ぬぐ">拭</ruby>って冴子は洋介に<ruby rubyText="ただ">質</ruby>した。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「本当にこれで」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おなじ苦しみをさせるなら、短い方がいい。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">それは後で良平にも分かる」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴子の心は吹っ切れた。</sentence>
<sentence>冴子はビデオをそっと床に置くと、手摺りに近づいた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「私も雲に乗れる？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「もちろんさ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">オレが受け止めてやる」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　洋介が腕を広げた。</sentence>
<sentence>急に洋介の体が大きくなった。</sentence>
<sentence>どんどん<ruby rubyText="ふく">膨</ruby>らんで、冴子の視界を埋め尽くした。</sentence>
<sentence>明るい光が洋介の体全体から放射されていた。</sentence>
<sentence>冴子は<ruby rubyText="あん">安</ruby><ruby rubyText="ど">堵</ruby>に包まれた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おいで…もう心の不安から解放される」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　冴<sampling type="end" />子は<ruby rubyText="ためら">躊躇</ruby>いもなく手摺りを乗り越えた。</sentence>
</paragraph>
</article>
</sample>
